304
00:21:17,538 --> 00:21:18,973
Wanna know where Suenaga is?

305
00:21:20,774 --> 00:21:21,875
What?

306
00:21:21,942 --> 00:21:23,577
<i>So you don't know, huh?</i>

307
00:21:23,644 --> 00:21:27,648
It was going around.
