308
00:21:28,549 --> 00:21:31,452
<i>I saw Runa whispering</i>
<i>about it with her friends.</i>

309
00:21:32,419 --> 00:21:35,489
<i>I feel sorry that they're keeping</i>
<i>you in the dark.</i>

310
00:21:35,556 --> 00:21:38,759
