311
00:21:38,826 --> 00:21:42,196
<i>I'll send you a picture. Anyway, bye.</i>

312
00:21:48,769 --> 00:21:49,870
What's up?

313
00:21:51,739 --> 00:21:53,741
KOMIYA DAI-ICHI ELEMENTARY

314
00:22:04,051 --> 00:22:06,253
I was gonna tell you about this today.

315
00:22:07,321 --> 00:22:08,622
But, you know,

