00:22:44,423 --> 00:22:45,590
<i>The school?</i>

321
00:23:15,020 --> 00:23:17,923
KOMIYA BRIDGE

322
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:28,233
KOMIYA DAI-ICHI ELEMENTARY

323
00:24:06,738 --> 00:24:07,906
Kuroiwa?

