00:24:10,475 --> 00:24:11,610
Is that you?

325
00:24:12,644 --> 00:24:13,712
Remember me?

326
00:24:14,813 --> 00:24:16,648
I guess not.

327
00:24:16,715 --> 00:24:17,883
You're her…

328
00:24:24,356 --> 00:24:27,092
You came to see Hijiri?
