329
00:24:32,164 --> 00:24:34,399
Those three years
really made a difference.

330
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:36,902
What?

331
00:24:36,968 --> 00:24:37,836
Nothing.

332
00:24:46,845 --> 00:24:47,712
Huh?

333
00:24:48,213 --> 00:24:49,047
You're leaving?

334
00:24:51,983 --> 00:24:54,252
