335
00:24:54,753 --> 00:24:55,954
So why'd you come?

336
00:24:59,124 --> 00:25:02,294
I just learned that she was here today.

337
00:25:03,195 --> 00:25:04,262
So I rushed here.

338
00:25:10,802 --> 00:25:12,904
Could you stay away from Hijiri?

339
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:16,441
Hijiri

340
00:25:18,843 --> 00:25:19,844
has me.

