00:26:36,187 --> 00:26:37,055
What's wrong?

348
00:26:38,323 --> 00:26:39,224
Where's your mom?

349
00:26:49,701 --> 00:26:50,535
Hey.

350
00:26:51,736 --> 00:26:53,505
