mushroom pasta I make all the time.

354
00:27:11,623 --> 00:27:12,557
Dig in.

355
00:27:14,159 --> 00:27:14,993
Here.

356
00:27:22,834 --> 00:27:23,668
Let's eat.

357
00:27:27,172 --> 00:27:28,139
It's yummy.

358
00:27:28,773 --> 00:27:29,607
You like it?

359
00:27:50,395 --> 00:27:53,531
MS. TACHIBANA,
I'M SORRY FOR LEAVING THIS NOTE

360
00:27:53,598 --> 00:27:55,567
SUENAGA

361
00:28:06,076 --> 00:28:08,511
-Who's she?
-One of my students.

362
00:28:09,412 --> 00:28:12,983
